xample:** **Parag Parikh Flexi Cap Fund** or **SBI Flexi Cap Fund**.\n    *   **Rationale:** Offers the fund manager flexibility to invest in large, mid, and small-cap stocks based on market opportunities. Ideal for capital appreciation over a long period (>5 years).\n\n**Disclaimer:** *The mentioned funds are for illustrative purposes only and are not direct recommendations. Please consult with a registered financial advisor before making any investment decisions. Past performance is not indicative of future returns.*"}, "agent": "Fixed Income Agent"}], "workflow_json": {"job_id": "27c7b9b2-6822-44d9-9d7f-a6c87a8a6e32", "report_timestamp": "20260409_181403", "started_at": "2026-04-09T17:55:47.348223+00:00", "completed_at": "2026-04-09T18:14:03.950440+00:00", "duration_seconds": 1096.602, "provider": "ollama_generate_multi_agent", "model": "deepseek-v3.1:671b-cloud", "base_url": "https://ollama.com/api", "usage_totals": {"prompt_eval_count": 37557, "eval_count": 41703}, "agent_runs": [{"agent": "Manager Agent", "focus": "Coordinate all agent findings into a coherent strategy.", "duration_seconds": 56.898, "response_chars": 8363, "usage": {"prompt_eval_count": 290, "eval_count": 2127, "total_duration": 55810238078, "load_duration": null, "prompt_eval_duration": null, "eval_duration": null}}, {"agent": "Data Collection Agent", "focus": "Extract and structure all relevant financial facts from the input.", "duration_seconds": 51.441, "response_chars": 8024, "usage": {"prompt_eval_count": 293, "eval_count": 2020, "total_duration": 50022981166, "load_duration": null, "prompt_eval_duration": null, "eval_duration": null}}, {"agent": "Data Analyst Agent", "focus": "Analyze financial patterns, surplus, and optimization opportunities.", "duration_seconds": 71.419, "response_chars": 8866, "usage": {"prompt_eval_count": 292, "eval_count": 2230, "total_duration": 69607475093, "load_duration": null, "prompt_eval_duration": null, "eval_duration": null}}, {"agent": "Debt Management 